title: WATCH: Disney Cover Band Makes Couples Kiss in Washington Square Park
text:
WATCH: Disney Cover Band Makes Couples Kiss in Washington Square Park By Danielle Tcholakian | October 9, 2015 2:21pm Twitter Facebook Email More 
In a video posted to YouTube on Friday, a self-described Disney cover band called the Little Mermen hit Washington Square Park, descending on any pair that appeared to be a (heterosexual) couple and urging the male half to "kiss the girl." 
Watch and cringe.
